    "biography": "<p>This beast resembles a great cat, except that it has six legs and a pair of long, whiplike tentacles sprouting from its shoulders. Its pelt has a hideous blue-black sheen, and its eyes glow with an awful green balefulness.</p><p>A light-bending glamer continually surrounds a displacer beast, making it difficult to surmise the creature's true location.</p>",
